    新臺幣5萬元以下罰金；透過電子媒體或網路方式為之者，\r\n    亦同。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CYDM/111%2c%e6%99%ba%e7%b0%a1%2c20%2c20220829%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CYDM,111,智簡,20,20220829,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"智簡","JNO":"20","JDATE":"20220829","JTITLE":"違反商標法"}